### 자모 검색
POST http://localhost:9200/ac_test4/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"query" : {
		"bool" : {
			"should" : [{
				"term" : {
					"itemJamo" : "ㅅㅣㄴㅎ"
				}
			}],
			"minimum_should_match" : 1
		}
	}
}

